tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE keyword_performance (
    campaign_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    keyword VARCHAR(255),
    impressions INT,
    clicks INT,
    cost FLOAT,
    conversions INT
);

CREATE TABLE Keyword_Performance (
    keyword_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id UUID,
    keyword_name STRING,
    clicks INT,
    impressions INT,
    spend DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE Ad_Spend (
    ad_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id UUID,
    ad_name STRING,
    ad_spend DECIMAL,
    date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE keyword_performance (
  keyword_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  keyword VARCHAR(255),
  campaign_id INT,
  ad_spend DECIMAL,
  clicks INT,
  impressions INT
);

CREATE TABLE keyword_performance (
    keyword_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    keyword_name VARCHAR(255),
    campaign_id INT,
    clicks INT,
    impressions INT,
    conversions INT
);

CREATE TABLE campaigns (
    campaign_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name VARCHAR(255),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    budget DECIMAL(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE ad_groups (
    ad_group_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    ad_group_name VARCHAR(255),
    campaign_id INT,
    max_bid DECIMAL(8, 2),
    status VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE ads (
    ad_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    ad_text VARCHAR(500),
    ad_group_id INT,
    cost DECIMAL(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE keyword_campaigns (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    keyword VARCHAR(255),
    campaign_name VARCHAR(255),
    clicks INT,
    impressions INT,
    cost DECIMAL(10,2)
);

CREATE TABLE ads (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    ad_name VARCHAR(255),
    ad_group_id INT,
    ad_text VARCHAR(255),
    clicks INT,
    impressions INT,
    cost DECIMAL(10,2),
    FOREIGN KEY (ad_group_id) REFERENCES ad_groups(id)
);

CREATE TABLE campaigns (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name VARCHAR(255),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    budget DECIMAL(10,2)
);
